based on value type will fix
declare the varibles is compasory these programs are called static typed lang
declare the varibles is not required these programs are called dynamic  typed lang
set or group of statements is called program
============================
lang translator 
it is software
it is used to convert high level to low level 
these are 2 types
	compiler
	it is used to convert high level to low level to entire pogram once
	ex:c,java
	interpretor
			it is used to convert high level to low level to one by one pogram once
				ex:python,js.
				
				
