while
===========================
while loop: the group of statement's are excuted repetly until condition return true
if return false then to stop the while loop

synatx:

while condition:
	st-1
	st-2
	st-3
print('gm/n'*5)

while is a keyword
condition is a relational expression it return true/false
':' brgining of the while loop
st1,st2,----body of while loop
